desc: Maewenn Designs is a timeless collection of nature and art-inspired jewellery, designed and crafted by talented local designers all over the world or by Maewenn herself. Maewenn Designs was founded by Maewenn in 2012 with a sole purpose to create a unique hand-crafted jewellery brand at affordable prices.

layout.text: A collection of artistic and elegant jewellery designs, lovingly inspired by nature and hand-crafted with care.
